Property.name: DraughtLevel
Property.description: The measure of the draught level of this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: ForwardDraughtLevel
Property.description: The draught level measured at the fore end of this transport means.

Property.name: AftDraughtLevel
Property.description: The draught level measured at the aft end of this transport means.

Property.name: Helipad
Property.description: The indication of whether or not there is a helipad on this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: ManoeuvringSpeed
Property.description: The manoeuvring speed measured for this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: PilotageExemption
Property.description: The identifier of a pilotage exemption for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: SailingAdviceNotificationInformation
Property.description: Sailing advice notification information, expressed as text, for this logistics transport movement.

Relationship.name: VoyageLifecycle
Relationship.description: The state lifecycle of a trasnport movement

Property.name: DriverAccompanied
Property.description: The indication of whether or not this logistics means of transport is accompanied by a driver.

TransportEvent.name: TransportEvent
TransportEvent.description: A significant occurrence or happening during transport.

Property.name: Type
Property.description: The code specifying the type of transport event.

Property.name: OccurrenceTime
Property.description: The actual date, time, date time, or other date time value of the occurrence of this transport event.

Property.name: ReportedTime
Property.description: The date, time, date time or other date time value of the actual arrival related to this transport event.

Property.name: Description
Property.description: The textual description of this transport event.

Relationship.name: CertifyingTradeParty
Relationship.description: A certifying party for this transport event.

Relationship.name: RelatedLocation
Relationship.description: The location of a conveyance facility related to this transport event.

Relationship.name: EventLocation
Relationship.description: The logistics location where this transport event occurs.

Relationship.name: RelatedTransportRoute
Relationship.description: The route related to this transport event.

TransportMovement.name: TransportMovement
TransportMovement.description: The conveyance (physical carriage) of goods or other objects used for logistics transport purposes.

Property.name: Identification
Property.description: The unique identifier for this logistics transport movement, such as a voyage number, flight number, or trip number.

Property.name: TerminalOperatorAssignedIdentification
Property.description: A unique identifier for this logistics transport movement as assigned by a terminal operator.

Property.name: Stay
Property.description: The unique identifier of a stay in a port, airport or other place of service for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Status
Property.description: The code specifying a status for the logistics transport movement, such as estimated or final.

Property.name: Mode
Property.description: The code specifying the mode, such as by air, sea, rail, road or inland waterway, for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Stage
Property.description: The code specifying the stage of this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: CargoDescription
Property.description: The textual description of the cargo for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Closing
Property.description: The date, time, date time, or other date time value by which cargo should be loaded onto the means of transport for the departure of this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Information
Property.description: Information, expressed as text, for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: DangerousGoods
Property.description: The indication of whether or not dangerous goods are carried for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: ManifestOnboard
Property.description: The indication of whether or not the manifest for this logistics transport movement is onboard.

Property.name: TransitDirection
Property.description: The code specifying the transit direction of this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: TransportEquipment
Property.description: The number of pieces of transport equipment for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Package
Property.description: The number of packages in this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Consignment
Property.description: The number of consignments in this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Crew
Property.description: The number of crew members for this logistics transport movement.

Property.name: Passenger
Property.description: The number of passengers for this logistics transport movement.

Relationship.name: ActualEvent
Relationship.description: A transport event specified for this logistics transport movement.

Relationship.name: UsedTransportMeans
Relationship.description: The means of transport used for this logistics transport movement.

LogisticsLocation.name: LogisticsLocation
LogisticsLocation.description: A logistics related physical location or place.

Property.name: OtherIdentification
Property.description: A unique identifier for this logistics related location, such as a United Nations Location Code (UNLOCODE) or GS1 Global Location Number (GLN).

Property.name: Name
Property.description: A name, expressed as text, of this logistics related location.

Property.name: Description
Property.description: A textual description of this logistics related location.

Property.name: Country
Property.description: The unique identifier of a country for this logistics location.

Property.name: Type
Property.description: A code specifying the type of this logistics related location.

Relationship.name: PostalTradeAddress
Relationship.description: The postal trade address information for this logistics related location.

TransportMeans.name: TransportMeans
TransportMeans.description: The devices used to convey goods or other objects from place to place during logistics cargo movements.

Property.name: Identification
Property.description: An identifier of this logistics means of transport, such as the International Maritime Organization number of a vessel.

Property.name: Name
Property.description: The name, expressed as text, of this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: CargoGrossWeight
Property.description: The measure of the total gross weight (mass) of all cargo loaded onto this logistics means of transport, including packaging but excluding any associated transport equipment.

Property.name: Conference
Property.description: The code specifying the conference for this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: GrossWeight
Property.description: The measure of the gross weight (mass) of this logistics means of transport including cargo, such as the measure of the overall size of a vessel determined in accordance with the provisions of the International Convention on Tonnage Measurement of Ships, 1969.

Property.name: ISPSSecurityLevel
Property.description: The code specifying the International Ship and Port facility Security (ISPS) level assigned to this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: Length
Property.description: The measure of the length of this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: LoadedCargo
Property.description: The measure of the cargo loaded onto this logistics means of transport, such as the number of barrels of oil or other quantity of breakbulk cargo.

Property.name: NetWeight
Property.description: The measure of the net weight (mass) of this logistics means of transport, such as the net tonnage of a vessel determined in accordance with the provisions of the International Convention on Tonnage Measurement of Ships, 1969.

Property.name: RequiredLaneLength
Property.description: The measure of the external length required in a lane for this logistics transport means.

Property.name: Sequence
Property.description: The sequence number differentiating this logistics transport means from others.

Property.name: Type
Property.description: The code specifying the type of logistics means of transport (Reference UNECE Recommendation 28).

Property.name: TypeText
Property.description: The type, expressed as text, of this logistics means of transport.

Property.name: WasteReportingExemption
Property.description: The indication of whether or not there is a waste reporting exemption for this logistics means of transport.

Relationship.name: RegistrationTransportEvent
Relationship.description: A registration event of this logistics transport means.

TransportRoute.name: TransportRoute
TransportRoute.description: A way or course taken from one location to another for the purpose of transporting cargo and or passengers.

Property.name: Identification
Property.description: The unique identifier of this transport route.

Property.name: DeparturePoint
Property.description: A departure point, expressed as text, for this transport route.

Property.name: Description
Property.description: The textual description of this transport route.

Property.name: FrequencyType
Property.description: The code specifying the type of frequency for this transport route, such as weekly, bi-monthly or daily.

Property.name: Map
Property.description: Binary object data that is the map of this transport route.

Property.name: Status
Property.description: The code specifying a status for a transport route, such as planned or actual.

Property.name: TransportMeans
Property.description: A means of transport, expressed as text, for this transport route.

Relationship.name: ItineraryStopLocation
Relationship.description: An itinerary stop event for this transport route, such as a port call in a vessel schedule.
